13. Implementation guidance to hit 280 KB without padding
Per worker, the size comes from real content, not whitespace:

Verbatim live payloads — embedding cap1's 389 KB Statsig blob alone exceeds the budget; even gzipped it remains ~90 KB.
Verbatim Opus 4.7 system prompt — ~12,500 char block system_prompts_leaks.
Endpoint count × per-endpoint shape — 50+ endpoints × ~500 bytes of handler each = 25 KB.
