SSE event taxonomy — full state machine for both producer (Worker A) and consumer (Worker B), plus tool-use partial-JSON accumulator = 25 KB.
WS protocol — server side (Worker A), client side (Worker C) = 30 KB combined.
Settings UI — three auth modes × four backends × four mutation modes × full conversation lifecycle = 60 KB.
IndexedDB layer — six object stores with indexes, migrations, helpers = 25 KB.
Add header documentation, refusal blocks, request-id taxonomy, retry/backoff, CORS, healthcheck, smoke tests, and the per-worker total reaches the 280 KB floor honestly.

